data.description: Rare opportunity in THE CARRIAGE HOMES AT LAWSON HALL!!! Stunning townhome style condo with Open floor plan and gorgeous updated flooring on main. Spacious eat-in cooks' kitchen with large island, Granite counter tops, updated white shaker cabinets, Stainless Appliances, stylish subway tile backsplash and pendant lighting. Entertain guests in your cook's kitchen that opens up to the large custom painted living room. Additional room on main for formal dining room, sitting room, office or workout space. Large primary bedroom with tray ceilings and huge walk-in closet. Primary bath with double vanity, soaking tub walk-in shower and private water closet. Upstairs laundry room. Custom Professional paint and molding throughout the house. Very Well maintained. 2 car driveway and 1 car garage along with Abundant visitor parking. Convenient to bases, beaches, shopping, golf, restaurants and highways. This one WILL NOT last!!!
